  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK220">
<l>oppuravi ṉāṉvaruṅ kēṭeṉiṉ ṉaḵtoruvaṉ</l>
<l>viṟṟukkōṭ ṭakka tuṭaittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If it be said that loss will result from benevolence, such loss is worth being procured even by the sale of one's self.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
